                    <h3>Do I have to go to every event?</h3>
                    <p>
                        No, but you really should. For one thing, most events start where the previous event ended,
                        so if you skipped an event, you might have trouble finding your group. Or all the groups.
                        Also, every event has some purpose. By going to all of them, you'll learn your way around
                        campus, be in the F!rosh picture, see what the fuss is over the purple dye, and generally
                        meet more people and have more fun.
                    </p>

                    <h3>What's up with purple dye?</h3>
                    <p>
