                    </p>

                    <h3>What if I get hurt?</h3>
                    <p>
                        There will be members of Skule Patrol at every event and with every group. Skule Patrol
                        members are trained in first aid and will have first aid kits. They can be identified by
                        their snazzy red T-shirts.
